data.description: Welcome to your new 3 bed 2.5 bath home in the sought after Cobblestone neighborhood. This well-appointed and well-maintained home sits on an oversized lot in a private gated subdivision. Whether you enjoy cooking or entertaining, this beautiful home has so much to offer! Make your favorite meal to impress all in your gourmet kitchen with granite countertops, stainless appliances, large island and ample cabinet space. Take the party outside to the large yard and patio with no neighbors behind you. Enjoy games or movies? Transform the upstairs loft into a large game/media room for all your entertaining needs. Have kids or work remotely, the study downstairs would make a fantastic playroom or office for you. At the end of the day, it's about relaxing, and this fantastic home offers many ways to kick back and relax when needed. Do not miss out! Schedule your tour today before it's too late!
